---
description: Svelte 5 in legacy mode (no runes)
globs:
  - "src/**/*.svelte"
---

Do NOT use runes or set `<svelte:options runes={true}>`.
- Props: `export let ...`
- Reactivity: `$:` labels, not `$state/$derived/$effect/$props`.
- Events: `on:click`, `on:input` etc. (no `onclick` attributes in legacy files)
- Binding: `bind:value`, `bind:checked`, etc.
- Don’t touch `<style>` blocks unless asked.
